<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Todo List</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body class="bg-light">
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-primary justify-content-between">
            <a class="navbar-brand mx-3" href="/">
                {{#if isAuthenticated}}{{user.name}}'s {{/if}}
                Todo List
            </a>
            {{#if isAuthenticated}}
            <a href="/users/logout" class="btn btn-outline-light mx-3">Logout</a>
            {{else}}
            <a href="/users/login" class="btn btn-outline-light mx-3">Login</a>
            {{/if}}
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-8">
                    {{{ body}}}
                </div>

                <div class="col-4 mt-3">
                    <h3 class="text-center">使用說明</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>這是一個前端用bootstrap，後端用Express.js，資料庫用MongoDB的Todo List作品</li>
                        <li>可以自行註冊帳號或使用測試帳號（Email:123@123.123，password:123）登入使用</li>
                        <li>點擊畫面左上 Todo List 可以看到全部的 todo</li>
                        <li>點擊 Create 可新增一筆 todo</li>
                        <li>點擊 Detail 可進入詳細頁面，查看 todo</li>
                        <li>點擊 Edit 可進入修改頁面，修改 todo</li>
                        <li>點擊 Delete 可刪除該筆 todo</li>
                        <li>點擊畫面右上 Logout 可登出帳號</li>
                        <li>程式碼:
                            <a href="https://github.com/WuWeiTsung/AC-todolist-demo"
                                target="_blank">https://github.com/WuWeiTsung/AC-todolist-demo</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>